Flexible issue tracker allowing tracking of many styles including
classic bug tracking/TODO management, help desk, sales leads. Comes
with several templates and creating your own is straightforward.
Supports SQLite and PostgreSQL backends, offers UIs via web, email
cli and remote API. The web interface is easy to extend and there is
account and role-based access control.

Flavor:
        pgsql      - use a PostgreSQL backend
